criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Adult of 18 or over;

          -  fully and honestly informed, and not having reported his non-opposition to the use of
             his samples for research;

          -  Affiliated to a social security scheme;

          -  Hepatic and / or renal transplant stable between two and twenty-four months after
             transplantation, treated with tacrolimus;

          -  Without modification of immunosuppressive treatment or treatment likely to modify
             their pharmacokinetics (imidazoles, macrolides ...) during the last two weeks;

          -  Each patient can only be included once.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Participation in another protocol whose procedures are incompatible with the
             realization of the study;

          -  Pregnant woman ;

          -  Major person subject to legal protection (safeguard of justice, guardianship,
             tutorship);

          -  Person deprived of liberty;

          -  Opposition to the use of clinical data and remnants of samples taken from care for
             research purposes.
